title: Virusi itera SIDA yandurira mu guhuza amaraso n’umuntu ubana na Virusi itera SIDA binyuze mu gusangira inshinge, cyagwa ibindi bikomeretsa byagiyeho  amaraso yanduye.
content:
Virusi itera SIDA yandurira mu guhuza amaraso n’umuntu ubana na Virusi itera
SIDA binyuze mu gusangira inshinge, cyagwa ibindi bikomeretsa byagiyeho 
amaraso yanduye.
Iyo umwana apimwe cyangwa asuzumwe kare bikamenyekana ko yanduye 
virusi itera SIDA kandi agatangira imiti kare, bimwongerera amahirwe yo 
kurama no kugira ubuzima bwiza.
